name: Apparata Utility Packages
overview: This collection contains Apparata's open source utility packages.

packages.summary: Swift toolkit for working with binary data.
Swift experiment with composition based components.
Various convenient Swift code constructs. Some are experimental.
Swift data structure for node graph based apps.
RuleKit is a small framework for creating predicate rules that can be evaluated and used to e.g. filter arrays in a data driven way, without adding explicit if or switch statements to the code.
SequenceKit provides a number of composable, numeric Swift sequences.
A simple templating library written in Swift.
Simple wrapper for using SearchKit with Swift.
